      <ab><ab>Revāyat of Kama Bohra (MU1, p. 457) on the Yašt ī <em>gāϑābiiō</em>:</ab>
         <ab class="ab_indent">(Pers.) <em>āat̰ dīš āuuaēδaiiae.mahi.</em> negāh ruz māh <em>gāϑābiiō spəṇtābiiō. ratuxṣ̌aϑrābiiō. aṣ̌aōnebiiō. y. v. x. f. āat̰. ahunuuaitiiā̊. gāϑiiā̊. y. v. x. f.</em>.</ab>
         <ab class="ab_indent">(Pers.) "<em>āat̰ dīš āuuaēδaiiae.mahi.</em> (and then) he should consider the day and month (and recite): <em>gāϑābiiō spəṇtābiiō. ratuxṣ̌aϑrābiiō. aṣ̌aōnebiiō. y. v. x. f. āat̰. ahunuuaitiiā̊. gāϑiiā̊. y. v. x. f.</em>".</ab>
